===Recruiting===
BYU has signed five recruits for the 2014-15 season. Two of BYU's recruits will head out on their missions immediately and return for the 2016-17 season. Ryan Andrus, Jake Toolson,<ref name="Surprises">{{cite web|url=http://www.loyalcougars.com/2014/07/23/byu-basketball/5366-toolson-kaufusi-will-walk-on-for-byu-hoops-in-2014/|title=Toolson, Kaufusi will walk on for BYU hoops in 2014|publisher=USA Today via Loyal Cougars|accessdate=2014-07-23}}</ref> and Dalton Nixon<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ksl.com/?sid=30150421&nid=498&fm=most_popular|title=Nixon to play for BYU in 2014-15|publisher=KSL|accessdate=2014-06-02}}</ref> will play at least one season before heading out on missions. 
