===Transfers===
BYU introduces three new faces from transfers to the 2013-14 roster. Chase Fischer will be eligible to play immediately after sitting out as a redshirt from Wake Forest all last season. Jamal Aytes will be eligible to start playing for the Cougars after the fall semester ends, near the end of December. Kyle Davis also transferred from [[Utah State Aggies men's basketball|Utah State]] and will redshirt the 2014-15 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ksl.com/?nid=498&sid=29908932|title=Davis transferring from Utah State to BYU|publisher=KSL|accessdate=2014-05-15}}</ref>

